  "detailed_description": "Lux Ex is a one level game that brings back the classic arcade experience with no save games and limited chances on a vertical scrolling shooter. Can you beat it?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/776280/extras/a4a1cfb8528b12fd8b8c3c0f0081b2bc.poster.avif?t=1660083027\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/776280/extras/a4a1cfb8528b12fd8b8c3c0f0081b2bc.webm?t=1660083027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/776280/extras/a4a1cfb8528b12fd8b8c3c0f0081b2bc.mp4?t=1660083027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Destroy bugs and glitches in your astral body to recover data from the source of the light of your soul.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Procedurally Generated Waves</strong><br>Every playthrough is different. Memorizing the levels are not enough, you have to really LEARN how to play;<br><br></li><li><strong>Play it your own way -</strong><br>A wide assortment of weapons and powers that allows you to express yourself through play style;<br><br></li><li><strong>Dynamic difficulty -</strong><br>The game adapts to your skill level, so as you become a better player, the game gets more challenging;</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/776280/extras/6802b9762dd823059a20ec7ae3dc374a.avif?t=1660083027\" width=480 height=1474 /></span>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/776280/extras/a51d01eb0edb3c10fe7b231861421fac.avif?t=1660083027\" width=480 height=1250 /></span>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/776280/extras/ccbb491431e1006da89914725dcaa382.avif?t=1660083027\" width=482 height=482 /></span>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/776280/extras/3b144fd28df677690b7f21a24a18df8e.avif?t=1660083027\" width=482 height=480 /></span>.",
